{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-variables-and-operators/learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-d","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"top-learn-variables-and-operators","challengeType":15,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Postoje dva ograničenja za nazive parametara u JavaScript:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Ime mora da sadrži samo slova, brojeve ili simbole <code>$</code> i <code>_</code>.</li>\n<li>Prvo slovo ne sme da bude broj.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Primeri ispravnih imena:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let userName;\nlet test123;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Zanimljivo je – dolar znak <code>'$'</code> i podvučani <code>'_'</code> takođe mogu se koristiti u imenima. To su obični simboli, kao slova, bez bilo kakvog posebnog značenja.</p>\n<p>Ovi nazivi su važeći:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let $ = 1; // declared a variable with the name \"$\"\nlet _ = 2; // and now a variable with the name \"_\"\n\nconsole.log($ + _); // 3\n</code></pre>\n<p>Primeri neispravnih imena parametara:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let 1a; // cannot start with a digit\n\nlet my-name; // hyphens '-' aren't allowed in the name\n</code></pre>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Odin","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-variables-and-operators/learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-d"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koji od ovih je važeće ime parametra u JavaScript?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><code>let 2things;</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>let my-name;</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>let var!;</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>let $myVar;</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":4}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","tests":[],"title":"Naučite o parametrima i operaterima funkcije D","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/the-odin-project/#top-learn-variables-and-operators","dashedName":"learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-d","certification":"the-odin-project","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"top-learn-variables-and-operators","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-variables-and-operators/learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-e","prevChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-variables-and-operators/learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-c","id":"65e1985e500d930ce8ed90a7","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":15,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-variables-and-operators/learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-d"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}